{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"36ef851b50","title":"北京市革委会传达陈伯达的六点指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ff4369076b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":10,"articleId":"36ef851b50","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"革命委员会","id":"1d084c925f","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4c27050914","type":"title","text":"北京市革委会传达陈伯达的六点指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"36ef851b50","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9221b6f8a2","type":"paragraph","text":"1. 革命群众都必须坚决贯彻执行毛主席党中央“抓革命、促生产”的伟大指示，争取革命生产双丰收。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"36ef851b50","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dc5a9dda11","type":"paragraph","text":"2. 无产阶级专政机构的神圣任务，第一点保卫无产阶级文化大革命；第二点建立稳定无产阶级革命的秩序；第三点保护国家财产；第四点，保护革命群众中不同意见人的人身安全。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"36ef851b50","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8f510ed9d","type":"paragraph","text":"3. 不要武斗，禁止打、砸、抢、抓、抄。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"36ef851b50","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"abadf97d1f","type":"paragraph","text":"4. 煽动武斗的坏人，应受无产阶级专政国家的法律制裁。坏人煽动武斗的话，那坏人就暴露出来了，要追查坏人，要进行制裁。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"36ef851b50","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ba3d7560f1","type":"paragraph","text":"5. 破坏劳动纪律，不参加生产，到处游荡，自由跑入跑出，扰乱革命生产秩序的，工厂一律不发给工资，农村人民公社一律不给记工分，机关也一样。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"36ef851b50","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a56cb7221d","type":"paragraph","text":"6. 要依靠群众，光依靠无产阶级专政机关是不行的，公安部门一定要依靠群众才有权威。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"36ef851b50","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}